README – ShapeStar Controller (GPLv3 License Notice)

Software Information
---------------------
ShapeStar Controller is a CNC control software developed by ShapeStar Technologies, based on open-source gSender and GRBLHAL projects. 
It is specifically designed and optimized for the ShapeStar SS Pro CNC milling machine to provide a reliable, user-friendly, and license-compliant control interface.

Copyright (C) 2025 ShapeStar Technologies


