Included Components
-------------------
The software is built upon the following open-source components:

Component               License   Source
-------------------------------------------------------------
gSender                 GPLv3     https://github.com/Sienci-Labs/gsender
GRBLHAL Firmware        GPLv3     https://github.com/grblHAL
ShapeStar Controller UI GPLv3     © 2025 ShapeStar Technologies


Summary of Modifications
------------------------
- Customized UI to match the ShapeStar brand identity.
- Redesigned calibration and setup wizards.
- Added “Probe-less Zeroing” and “Angular Correction” functions.
- Integrated Wi-Fi connection management and joystick control support.


